  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Envelope is a psychological thriller game that puts you in the shoes of an unfortunate soul who finds himself getting pushed to do something beyond anything he could possibly imagine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into a small open world where you choose your path, and your choices matter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/d7886a2abe07abe45095dff3351446b1.webp?t=1763140703\" width=600 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive gameplay and storytelling. Work your way through the night shift to explore an odd world full of strange people.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not let the mundane tasks fool you, there is something sinister going on, and you somehow end up in the middle of it all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/e0ef64b2243d8a8160e49361f21365a7.poster.avif?t=1763140703\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/e0ef64b2243d8a8160e49361f21365a7.webm?t=1763140703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/e0ef64b2243d8a8160e49361f21365a7.mp4?t=1763140703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/b07a63b3dddc82a919cab15805379b58.webp?t=1763140703\" width=600 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The second part of the game reveals an open world for you to explore, and every choice you make could affect how the ending of the game plays out.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the main objective, or take an alternate route to explore what the world has to offer. There are plenty of interesting characters to come by. Maybe you'll even find one of the many secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/dd2a2895c00373e0c7385f182af1556f.poster.avif?t=1763140703\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/dd2a2895c00373e0c7385f182af1556f.webm?t=1763140703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/dd2a2895c00373e0c7385f182af1556f.mp4?t=1763140703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/621a5d3fb962ac27e1a67d2d4c2be7ca.webp?t=1763140703\" width=600 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Regardless of how your mission ends, your actions will progress the game, making future attempts quicker and easier.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock additional items, shortcuts, or abilities by completing certain tasks. Even if you die, your actions have permanently altered the world, allowing you to return stronger than ever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/d15743f1fdf85dc0e23476623eb63ad0.poster.avif?t=1763140703\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/d15743f1fdf85dc0e23476623eb63ad0.webm?t=1763140703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/d15743f1fdf85dc0e23476623eb63ad0.mp4?t=1763140703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple endings</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Freedom of choice</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your actions permanently change the world to give you more tools with each attempt</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minimalistic indie chic graphic style inspired by the Nintendo 64</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strange characters that may or may not help you on your journey</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Two separate storylines intersecting in the strangest way possible</strong></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Envelope is a psychological thriller game that puts you in the shoes of an unfortunate soul who finds himself getting pushed to do something beyond anything he could possibly imagine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into a small open world where you choose your path, and your choices matter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/d7886a2abe07abe45095dff3351446b1.webp?t=1763140703\" width=600 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive gameplay and storytelling. Work your way through the night shift to explore an odd world full of strange people.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not let the mundane tasks fool you, there is something sinister going on, and you somehow end up in the middle of it all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/e0ef64b2243d8a8160e49361f21365a7.poster.avif?t=1763140703\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/e0ef64b2243d8a8160e49361f21365a7.webm?t=1763140703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/e0ef64b2243d8a8160e49361f21365a7.mp4?t=1763140703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2717480/extras/b07a63b3dddc82a919cab15805379b58.webp?t=1763140703\" width=600 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragra